{"tid":2013983,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"身體變差但搵唔到原因真係好令人迷惘","createTime":"2020-05-12T16:33:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T21:11:17.000Z","uid":36329,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"673fed09c899b51248f80e7b6d5083ba08581082","tid":2013983,"uid":36329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:33:45.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n老竇今年57歲 都差唔多六張嘢<br />\n身體冇咁健康其實都預咗<br />\n年頭個陣夾硬拉咗佢去做身體檢查<br />\n糖尿中央肥胖脂肪肝驗曬出來<br />\n本身又有高血壓<br />\n於是老竇就開始調整飲食<br />\n雖然一開始佢會好燥底 成日都想破戒<br />\n不過keep咗一排血糖指數又靚仔返<br />\n<br />\n然後佢又開始戒煙<br />\n老竇從來都冇係屋企食過煙<br />\n所以我諗佢都唔係重度煙民<br />\n但係唔知關唔關戒煙嘅過程事<br />\n佢依排周身關節痛 手掌又腫曬成日會麻痺<br />\n又皮膚痕頭痕冇胃口<br />\n有時又會個頭暈 以為係血壓丸問題但佢食緊嘅血壓藥本身劑量已經好低<br />\n睇過私家診所甚至骨科醫生都完全醫唔好啲痛症<br />\n個人完全冇曬心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上星期五去咗抽血驗類風濕 依家都未有結果 總覺得好不安<br />\n<br />\n骨科照完X光話佢唔係椎間盤突出（佢以前試過都做過手術）<br />\n另一個醫生就話如果驗血報告話唔係類風濕可能就係純粹關節勞損<br />\n但點解勞損會手腫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上網睇類風濕關節炎係不可逆嘅病 希望唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人身邊有人經歷過類似情況可以參考下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e87609847df461955cab17bc7fc3c0d341e5ec60","tid":2013983,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:36:33.000Z","msg":"食返煙會唔會冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇食過唔知"},{"pid":"bb03faa311681af6a5d0045a91dfbd91de8c2311","tid":2013983,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:36:49.000Z","msg":"有冇食戒煙香口膠"},{"pid":"25850d0044ccda3336dbfea384d553547e52d163","tid":2013983,"uid":322769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:37:54.000Z","msg":"食開真係由佢"},{"pid":"dea530d68fcbcf3ed4654b9ef2d159f5b3b1ff9e","tid":2013983,"uid":36329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e87609847df461955cab17bc7fc3c0d341e5ec60","tid":2013983,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:36:33.000Z","msg":"食返煙會唔會冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇食過唔知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:41:05.000Z","msg":"我都未食過<br />\n但以前老竇後生溝我呀媽個陣都戒過一次<br />\n之後會食返係因為後來成日要去中国出差<br />\n要應酬個陣就會食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知後生同老咗戒煙會唔會有分別<br />\n但我又好難開口叫佢食返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb4977e0c6547155158d585d9915887f23599e4","tid":2013983,"uid":305058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e87609847df461955cab17bc7fc3c0d341e5ec60","tid":2013983,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:36:33.000Z","msg":"食返煙會唔會冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇食過唔知"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:41:49.000Z","msg":"聽講話食好耐煙嘅<br />\n一停唔食就周身唔聚財<br />\n身體會有其他毛病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以寧願食番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"863fd58f7f71c659dec5901929f4992f58dab4bf","tid":2013983,"uid":36329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb03faa311681af6a5d0045a91dfbd91de8c2311","tid":2013983,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:36:49.000Z","msg":"有冇食戒煙香口膠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:42:15.000Z","msg":"冇<br />\n佢未真係開始戒煙個陣<br />\n平時星期六日全日係屋企可以完全唔食都冇乜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"470fe4a7efb1e24cca60d4b2665ae0947dde1c2c","tid":2013983,"uid":36329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adb4977e0c6547155158d585d9915887f23599e4","tid":2013983,"uid":305058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e87609847df461955cab17bc7fc3c0d341e5ec60","tid":2013983,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:36:33.000Z","msg":"食返煙會唔會冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\"